								<p>Harness the full power of rich media mobile advertising with Phluant’s dynamic Ninja format. Using assassin-like skills, the Ninja can detect user devices, operating systems, geolocation, and DMAs to deliver targeted content. It can pull in weather, traffic, news or other data feeds to tailor and sequence messages. Dynamic pricing and inventory pulled from nearby store locations drive shoppers into brick and mortar stores and bring them one step closer to a point of sale by enticing them to click. With the Ninja, content can be determined on the fly, and data is always up to date.</p>

