	<div class="section about" id="about">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="header one-half m-top-60">
				<div class="summary-dark-bg">
					learn more
					<span>about us</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="clear"></div>
			<div class="summary-small-dark-bg m-top-50 m-bottom-45">
				we are a mobile advertising platform that <span> solves the accountability of media spend </span> for agencies, publishers and clients direct.
			</div>
			<div class="clear"></div>
			<div class="two-third m-bottom-40">
				<p>
				 We offer a single platform which aggregates a number of otherwise fragmented products; including: a mobile ad server; mobile rich media ad formats and features and in-depth mobile analytics.
<BR><BR>
Our leading mobile rich media and display capabilities service the most innovative and inspiring mobile campaigns. Our ad platform allows agencies and publishers to monetize mobile advertising in a way that propels advertisers to shift ad spending to mobile, and extend how they communicate with their audience.  With industry-leading tools and close collaboration, we help our clients achieve dramatic, measurable results.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="one-third last m-bottom-40">
